\\par
## 9. Troubleshooting Quick Notes\\par
1. Auth popup rejects valid user\\par
- Confirm pincode is set for selected user profile.\\par
\\par
2. Credit sale not appearing in Pending Payments\\par
- Verify due amount > 0 and sale saved successfully.\\par
\\par
3. Invoice link not opening expected data\\par
- Recheck whether due type is sale vs purchase and linked invoice number.\\par
\\par
4. Summary cash mismatch\\par
- Reconcile with formula shown on Sales page and ensure all pending payments were entered on same date.\\par
\\par
---\\par
\\par
## 10. Go-Live Checklist\\par
1. All critical tests in Section 7 passed.\\par
2. At least one full end-to-end day simulation completed.\\par
3. User pincodes configured for all salesmen.\\par
4. Opening stock validated.\\par
5. Client trained on Daily Operational Flow.\\par
6. Backup policy confirmed.\\par
\\par
---\\par
\\par
## 11. Support Notes\\par
For support tickets, always include:\\par
1. Page name\\par
2. Invoice number (if applicable)\\par
3. Due ID (if pending payment issue)\\par
4. Screenshot/video\\par
5. Exact steps and expected vs actual result\\par
}
